name: Transition - Into My world [ stage ] -
description:
This is the collaboration works between Hans Kristo as Pop surrealist artist and Lucy Enigma ( Virtual Musician ) . This Psychedelic pop songs by Lucy Enigma is titled "Transitions" and was intepreted by Hans Kristo as a transition into the world of Lucy itself and a new stage (world) as well a new era . 

Written, Composed, Vocals  and instruments by Anggi @asteraspace#4926
Recorded at Kanawa Record Yogyakarta
Mixing & Mastering by Aloysiusnitia @AloysiusNitia
Studio Engineer by Kemal Akbar
Original Lucy Enigma MV art by Pram @apluswav

Intepretation MV / Tribute  (collaboration Music video) by Hans Kristo
